Title: The Television's Been Hijacked! A Live Broadcast of the Cell Games Press Conference
Writer: Aya Matsui, Katsuyuki Sumizawa, Akira Toriyama
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Hiromi Tsuru
Plot: Trunks informs the Z-Fighters of the tournament planned by Cell, and Android 16 is taken to Capsule Corporation to be repaired. Meanwhile, Goku and Gohan continue to train.
